IRC
	Internet Relay Chat
	Decentralized (sort of)

History
	Created in 1988
	Still going string

Pumping Station One
	irc://freenode.net/#pumpingstationone

Getting connected to ps1 IRC
	step one: install pidgin
	step 2
	Accounts >> Manage Accounts >> Add

Protocol: IRC
Username: your_nick_name
Server: irc.freenode.net
click Add

Joining The PS1 Chat Room
	Buddies >> Add Chat
	Account (you@irc.freenode.net (IRC)
	Channel: #pumpingstationone
	[X] Autojoin when account connects.
	[X] Remain in chat after window is closed.


